         <OBJECT_CONTRACT>
            <TITLE>
               <P>Replacing water mains and repairs to water mains to Council Housing and ex-Council houses</P>
            </TITLE>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="44161200"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="WORKS"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>The work comprises of replacing water mains and repairs to water mains to Council Housing and sold ex-Council houses.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">4800000</VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="44161200"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <n2016:NUTS CODE="UKL23"/>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>The Employer requires contractors on the framework to replace water mains and service pipes at 1,344 properties. Around 45 % of these properties have been sold and are occupied by owner occupiers. The remainder are tenanted properties owned by the Council.</P>
                  <P>The water mains and service pipes are mainly (but not always) located in the rear gardens of the properties which are connected in blocks to a single underground stop tap. On some of these properties a WRAS approved insulated duct will be used as a means of getting the water supply into the property where new kitchens have been installed.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <AC_QUALITY>
                  <AC_CRITERION>Quality</AC_CRITERION>
                  <AC_WEIGHTING>30</AC_WEIGHTING>
               </AC_QUALITY>
               <AC_PRICE>
                  <AC_WEIGHTING>70</AC_WEIGHTING>
               </AC_PRICE>
               <VAL_OBJECT CURRENCY="GBP">4800000</VAL_OBJECT>
               <DATE_START>2018-05-01</DATE_START>
               <DATE_END>2020-04-30</DATE_END>
               <RENEWAL/>
               <RENEWAL_DESCR>
                  <P>There is an option to extend for and additional 2 years.</P>
               </RENEWAL_DESCR>
               <NO_ACCEPTED_VARIANTS/>
               <NO_OPTIONS/>
               <NO_EU_PROGR_RELATED/>
            </OBJECT_DESCR>
         </OBJECT_CONTRACT>
